<h2>What&#x27;s New in 3.3.3.1</h2>
<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Codex: Reset countdown no longer exceeds the 5-hour window — reset times are now stored in ISO 8601 format, preventing a date-rollover bug that produced countdowns of up to 24 hours.</li>
</ul>
